comments.content:

please [run a search](http://web.archive.org/web/20110430161243/http:/www.google.com/search?q=site:typophile.com/node/%20masterfile) first. This came up a couple of times before.  
It’s custom by [Underware](http://web.archive.org/web/20110430161243/http:/www.underware.nl/site2/index.php?id1=underware&id2=custom-type&id3=logotypes&showthis=10).
